<lb ed="C I" n="0173a00"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><title>東平郡須昌縣□檀寺造經碑</title></jhead></juan>
<div2>
<lb ed="C I" n="0173a01"/><p id="pI01p0173a0101">大齊東<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">平</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">郡</unclear>須昌縣□檀寺碑</p>
</div2>
<div2>
<lb ed="C I" n="0173b01"/><p id="pI01p0173b0101">夫旨理<note n="0173001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30966;＝淵【史】</note><app n="0173001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">淵</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30966;</rdg></app>寂。凝然澄湛。百非不<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">能</unclear>非其非。千是無
<lb ed="C I" n="0173b02"/>以是其是。形言絕相。万像無能比其色。十<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">住</unclear>猶疑。
<lb ed="C I" n="0173b03"/>□<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">凡</unclear>情之所觀□。自非應說教門。真□叵顯。是以
<lb ed="C I" n="0173b04"/><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">降</unclear>神閻浮。曜靈光於羅衛。<note n="0173002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30967;＝戒【史】</note><app n="0173002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">戒</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30967;</rdg></app>風吹於大千。慈海流
<lb ed="C I" n="0173b05"/>於十域。慧鏡<note n="0173003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30334;＝照【史】</note><app n="0173003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">照</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30334;</rdg></app><unclear cert="low" reason="damage">愚</unclear>。若琉璃之現色影。魔道□心。有
<lb ed="C I" n="0173b06"/>緣皆益。攝影雙林。息障邁於千□□不疏體五住
<lb ed="C I" n="0173b07"/>之蹤。何能信矣。□佛弟子比丘法<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">慧</unclear>欲使<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">聖</unclear>教再
<lb ed="C I" n="0173b08"/>彰。神暉重朗。遠召□工。奉<note n="0173004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30369;＝剛【史】</note><app n="0173004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">剛</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30369;</rdg></app>彫玉。<note n="0173005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30968;＝置【史】</note><app n="0173005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">置</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30968;</rdg></app>靈尊於上堪。
<lb ed="C I" n="0173b09"/>剟觀音經於下□。願使　皇道竄<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">興</unclear>。父師常<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">樂</unclear>。邑
<lb ed="C I" n="0173b10"/>儀諸人。龍華初會。法界有形。等成正覺。其頌曰。
<lb ed="C I" n="0173b11"/>真趣幽微。弗可言宣。大慈垂訓。以教流傳。初演鹿
<lb ed="C I" n="0173b12"/>菀。靈鷲陳章。摧魔伏道。如日<app source="0173003" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">照</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30334;</rdg></app>霜。敬<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">造</unclear>□形。<app source="0173005" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">置</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB31167;</rdg></app>于
<lb ed="C I" n="0173b13"/>巖壑。刊經揚義。法流枯<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">涸</unclear>。
<lb ed="C I" n="0173b14"/>大齊皇建元年庚辰□九月己酉朔三日辛亥造經碑</p>
</div2>
